title: Crowds line up to visit ships for Fleet Week
text:
Photo: Michael Macor, The Chronicle The Navy Blue Angels fly past the steeple of St. Peter and Paul Church as they take to the skies over San Francisco Bay during Fleet Week in San Francisco , Calif., on Saturday, October 10, 2015. The Navy Blue Angels fly past the steeple of St. Peter and Paul...
The Navy ships docked at Pier 80 looked as they always had — but also different, crisper than the old photographs.
